title: 4 bed, 3 bath house for rent in Leander, Texas 78641
posting_body: Charming two story home in a well established neighborhood features a brick and stone elevation.
Open concept style floor plan is ideal for family living.
Kitchen boasts espresso cabinetry, equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite counters ,subway tile backsplash, ample storage with breakfast bar overlooking a bright living space.
Newly installed carpet, recent paint and tile flooring throughout.
Expansive second floor features versatile living space to include a large game room along with a spacious master suite with soaking tub, separate shower, dual vanity and secondary bedrooms.
Retreat to the outdoors, find a extended covered flagstone patio perfect for grilling and relaxing.
Access to the community amenities include swimming pool, covered pavilion, basketball court and much more.
A toll allowing for an easy commute and access to everything Cedar Park and Leander have to offer!
Renter responsible for utilities(Electric and water) and lawn care.
Last month's rent due at signing.
Must provide proof that tenant earns 3 times the rent amount.
